MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'HWAHAHAHAHAHAHA!'
Within lovely landscape of Sheep City - A crack ran through the ground and a strange being crawled out from under it. It is a huge monster, its whole body dripping with a strange mucus.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Mine name is Ω God! Preacher of true love...!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's something I absolutely cannot ignore.
Beside Khajuraho, who looked as if she is enduring a Captainache, Asahikawa stood stunned.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What is that? A demon...?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: God knows. Bro, get behind us just in case if you want to live.
Khajuraho, who for some reason calls me 'Bro', dropped her playful mood completely and raised her whip.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: And you too, little Pochy. You cannot die until you rescue your girlfriend safely and get laid together, right?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Thy said GIRLFRIEND--!?'
The fur covered monster that self-proclaimed as Ω God howled with its bloodshot eyeballs.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'ANSWER ME! IS THY LOVER OF THY SAME SEX!?'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Pochy
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'What? What? Um...?'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'If thy art a lover of the opposite sex, THY ART GUILTY! Mine shalt execute the heretic in name of the Ω God for indulging in sacrilegious and counterfeit love!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What? Can you stop using difficult words? Get to the point, what do you mean?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hmmm～ It seems that this Ω God, or whatever monster it is, is of a sect that says men should make love to men and women to women.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Sect, you said.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You're wrong! You can't force others to choose who they love because of their gender, age, status or race...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Heaven may forgive you, but I shalt not! Love is true love, no matter what it is...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You're so pointlessly cool right now.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That is religion! They're harsher on heresy than to paganism! If it's pagans, you can convert them so they can become your followers, but heretics are fundamentally enemies that can never understand...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: And so! That Ω God, who only allows homosexual love, is to me a despicable, spiteful heretic...!
Khajuraho radiated immensely threatening presence from her entire body as she confronted the Ω God. Really now, you're completely brave and cool from the usual--.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Oh, but don't get me wrong, okay? It doesn't mean I don't approve of love between homosexuals, okay? Both girl-to-girl and boy-to-boy are equally precious and naughty!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: So anything is fine as long as it's horny...?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Everyone's different and everyone's a pervert! That's my religion...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'GUILTY AS CHARGED--!'
Perhaps offended by Khajuraho's comment, Ω God raged and trembled in fury. At the same time, flesh-coloured tentacles extended from its entire body, smashing all the surrounding buildings.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'ABSURD! ABSURD! ABSURD! All love other than between of the same sex art counterfeit! Mine do not accept that it is love...!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Parallel lines. Figured. I'm an omnivore who'll take anything, even ghettos, and this Ω God can only put its ideal love in his mouth, unable to make up the difference in interpretation.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I kinda stopped understanding about what you two are saying from a while ago.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Still, you should at least know this. Look there...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Garw～, garw～...♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Sentosa♪ Love♪ Really love you...♪
Khajuraho indicated by tilting her chin that Jeran is licking Sentosa's cheek while they're both on the ground. Strangely it's a sight that's somewhat heartwarming rather than lewd--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What have they been doing since a while ago?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: They're making love.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: However. I don't care how friendly little Ranran is, but that shy Sento's actually flirting in public like that - That should never have happened.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Perhaps that Ω God is brainwashing and controlling Ranran and everyone else, forcing them to make love to each other.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Don't you feel like everyone's being forced to love each other of the same sex in that way? I know that, because I can do something similar.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It's a terrible power... I was also manipulated for a moment and I said and did some crazy things. Making them hug and kiss - It's pointless to force them to do that.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Dumbass, don't you basically always say things like that?
Ignoring Asahikawa's roasting, Khajuraho spoke thoughtfully.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Besides. Sento is an excellent sorceress, and she should be good at preventing that kind of mind-controlling magic and sorcery.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: And yet, ah, she's being manipulated as the Ω God pleases. Well, maybe she dropped her mental guard when she was approached by little Ranran and got upset.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That tiger girl and the lion girl were pretty good friends from the start.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: However. It wasn't to that extent, right?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Now those girls are abnormal, to say the least.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'They art not abnormal! This is the way love should be! Ahahahaha!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Men and men, women and women, love each other bravely! That's utopia! That is the ideal that humanity should aspire to!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I see. This Ω God with such distorted sexuality created its own ideal world it seems? A world where men only love men and women only love women--
As a result, in this small nation of demihumans, men and women live separately and have even built a wall in middle of the land to keep the opposite sex separated?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Likely. In other words, that Ω God or whatever it is, is the root of all evil. It is the source of the anomaly in this small nation of demihumans.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: In short, if that Ω God is exterminated, everything will be solved?
Probably. If that Ω God is the source of the Phantom Mist, then defeating it will end the anomaly - The usual.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Then let's do that. Even if it's a hassle.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: If I let this Ω God do what he wants, maybe Papa will only be able to love the same sex - men. Maybe he won't love me either.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I absolutely refuse to let that happen.
Asahikawa held up her gun with unusual seriousness and faced Ω God.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I can't allow not being loved by the person I want to love.
